<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Love The Way You Lie (Part II)"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Love The Way You Lie (Part II) - Pt. 2"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Eminem"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Rihanna"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Loud"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Loud (Deluxe)"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USUM71026644"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1440896205"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1442286440"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="21563004"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6M6lsQB4OhqL41eld29PeC"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="181228823"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Watercooling480"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:51.704"><div begin="0.389" end="4:51.704"><p begin="0.389" end="5.215" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0.389" end="0.635">On</span> <span begin="0.635" end="0.876">the</span> <span begin="0.876" end="1.409">first</span> <span begin="1.409" end="2.327">page</span> <span begin="2.537" end="2.801">of</span> <span begin="2.801" end="3.190">our</span> <span begin="3.190" end="5.215">story</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我们故事的开端</span></p><p begin="6.154" end="10.971" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="6.154" end="6.433">The</span> <span begin="6.433" end="7.919">future</span> <span begin="7.919" end="8.825">seemed</span> <span begin="8.935" end="9.324">so</span> <span begin="9.324" end="10.971">bright</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">未来似乎是那么地美好</span></p><p begin="11.868" end="16.821" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.868" end="12.223">Then</span> <span begin="12.223" end="12.418">this</span> <span begin="12.418" end="12.990">thing</span> <span begin="12.990" end="13.650">turned</span> <span begin="13.650" end="14.444">out</span> <span begin="14.730" end="15.087">so</span> <span begin="15.087" end="15.825">e</span><span begin="15.825" end="16.821">vil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可结局却很不幸</span></p><p begin="17.148" end="22.687" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.148" end="17.302">I</span> <span begin="17.302" end="17.517">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="17.517" end="17.990">know</span> <span begin="17.990" end="18.711">why</span> <span begin="18.711" end="19.477">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="19.477" end="20.204">still</span> <span begin="20.466" end="22.687">surprised</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不知为何我仍惊讶</span></p><p begin="23.426" end="29.306" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.426" end="23.977">Even</span> <span begin="23.977" end="25.225">angels</span> <span begin="25.225" end="25.960">have</span> <span begin="26.282" end="26.597">their</span> <span begin="26.597" end="27.884">wicked</span> <span begin="27.884" end="29.306">schemes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使天使也有邪恶的一面</span></p><p begin="29.485" end="35.247" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.485" end="29.939">And</span> <span begin="29.939" end="30.268">you</span> <span begin="30.268" end="30.912">take</span> <span begin="30.912" end="31.751">that</span> <span begin="32.069" end="32.406">to</span> <span begin="32.406" end="33.055">new</span> <span begin="33.055" end="35.247">extremes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你却淋漓尽致地把它发挥到极致</span></p><p begin="35.391" end="39.880" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.391" end="35.562">But</span> <span begin="35.562" end="35.728">you&apos;ll</span> <span begin="35.728" end="36.811">always</span> <span begin="36.811" end="37.473">be</span> <span begin="37.810" end="38.160">my</span> <span begin="38.160" end="39.880">hero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是你一直是我的英雄</span></p><p begin="40.374" end="45.094" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.374" end="41.118">Even</span> <span begin="41.118" end="42.026">though</span> <span begin="42.214" end="42.506">you&apos;ve</span> <span begin="42.506" end="43.490">lost</span> <span begin="43.613" end="43.981">your</span> <span begin="43.981" end="45.094">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使你已经失去理智</span></p><p begin="46.150" end="50.928" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.150" end="46.523">Just</span> <span begin="46.523" end="47.235">gonna</span> <span begin="47.235" end="47.972">stand</span> <span begin="47.972" end="48.297">there</span> <span begin="48.297" end="48.694">and</span> <span begin="48.694" end="49.288">watch</span> <span begin="49.288" end="49.711">me</span> <span begin="49.711" end="50.928">burn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就站在那里冷眼旁观我煎熬难耐</span></p><p begin="51.375" end="57.317" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="51.375" end="51.565">Well,</span> <span begin="51.565" end="51.899">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="51.899" end="52.685">al</span><span begin="52.685" end="53.418">right,</span> <span begin="53.418" end="54.079">because</span> <span begin="54.079" end="54.272">I</span> <span begin="54.272" end="54.845">like</span> <span begin="54.845" end="55.025">the</span> <span begin="55.025" end="55.639">way</span> <span begin="55.639" end="55.813">it</span> <span begin="55.813" end="57.317">hurts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系 因为我喜欢这心痛的感觉</span></p><p begin="57.702" end="1:02.449" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.702" end="58.027">Just</span> <span begin="58.027" end="58.761">gonna</span> <span begin="58.761" end="59.493">stand</span> <span begin="59.493" end="59.887">there</span> <span begin="59.887" end="1:00.191">and</span> <span begin="1:00.191" end="1:00.781">hear</span> <span begin="1:00.781" end="1:01.281">me</span> <span begin="1:01.281" end="1:02.449">cry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就站在那里冷眼旁观我泪眼婆娑</span></p><p begin="1:02.989" end="1:08.175" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.989" end="1:03.150">Well,</span> <span begin="1:03.150" end="1:03.493">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:03.493" end="1:04.238">al</span><span begin="1:04.238" end="1:05.005">right,</span> <span begin="1:05.005" end="1:05.659">because</span> <span begin="1:05.659" end="1:05.879">I</span> <span begin="1:05.879" end="1:06.433">love</span> <span begin="1:06.433" end="1:06.623">the</span> <span begin="1:06.623" end="1:07.056">way</span> <span begin="1:07.056" end="1:07.315">you</span> <span begin="1:07.315" end="1:08.175">lie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系 连你说谎都让我着迷</span></p><p begin="1:08.714" end="1:12.096" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.714" end="1:08.918">I</span> <span begin="1:08.918" end="1:09.282">love</span> <span begin="1:09.282" end="1:09.468">the</span> <span begin="1:09.468" end="1:10.115">way</span> <span begin="1:10.115" end="1:10.311">you</span> <span begin="1:10.311" end="1:12.096">lie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我喜欢你说谎的模样</span></p><p begin="1:12.509" end="1:17.185" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.509" end="1:14.007">Oh,</span> <span begin="1:14.546" end="1:14.714">I</span> <span begin="1:14.714" end="1:15.022">love</span> <span begin="1:15.022" end="1:15.211">the</span> <span begin="1:15.211" end="1:15.841">way</span> <span begin="1:15.841" end="1:16.023">you</span> <span begin="1:16.023" end="1:17.185">lie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我喜欢你说谎的模样</span></p><p begin="1:21.203" end="1:26.427" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.203" end="1:21.518">Now</span> <span begin="1:21.518" end="1:21.980">there&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:21.980" end="1:22.316">grav</span><span begin="1:22.316" end="1:23.079">el</span> <span begin="1:23.422" end="1:23.730">in</span> <span begin="1:23.730" end="1:24.437">our</span> <span begin="1:24.437" end="1:26.427">voices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻我们声音沙哑</span></p><p begin="1:26.530" end="1:31.262" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.530" end="1:26.866">Glass</span> <span begin="1:26.866" end="1:27.185">is</span> <span begin="1:27.185" end="1:28.726">shattered</span> <span begin="1:28.726" end="1:29.400">from</span> <span begin="1:29.820" end="1:30.108">the</span> <span begin="1:30.108" end="1:31.262">fight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">玻璃碎片四处散落</span></p><p begin="1:32.693" end="1:38.429" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.693" end="1:33.010">In</span> <span begin="1:33.010" end="1:33.393">this</span> <span begin="1:33.393" end="1:33.792">tug</span> <span begin="1:33.792" end="1:34.502">of</span> <span begin="1:34.502" end="1:35.262">war,</span> <span begin="1:35.577" end="1:35.885">you&apos;ll</span> <span begin="1:35.885" end="1:36.662">al</span><span begin="1:36.662" end="1:37.341">ways</span> <span begin="1:37.341" end="1:38.429">win</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们的拉锯战 你永远是赢家</span></p><p begin="1:38.769" end="1:42.948" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:38.769" end="1:40.295">Even</span> <span begin="1:40.295" end="1:41.044">when</span> <span begin="1:41.401" end="1:41.709">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:41.709" end="1:42.948">right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使我是对的</span></p><p begin="1:44.222" end="1:49.948" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.222" end="1:44.572">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:44.572" end="1:44.817">you</span> <span begin="1:44.817" end="1:45.356">feed</span> <span begin="1:45.356" end="1:45.937">me</span> <span begin="1:45.937" end="1:47.008">fa</span><span begin="1:47.162" end="1:47.441">bles</span> <span begin="1:47.441" end="1:48.247">from</span> <span begin="1:48.247" end="1:48.933">your</span> <span begin="1:48.933" end="1:49.948">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因你的谎言太彻底</span></p><p begin="1:50.298" end="1:55.960" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.298" end="1:50.704">With</span> <span begin="1:50.704" end="1:51.882">violent</span> <span begin="1:51.882" end="1:52.836">words</span> <span begin="1:52.943" end="1:53.271">and</span> <span begin="1:53.271" end="1:54.023">empt</span><span begin="1:54.023" end="1:54.517">y</span> <span begin="1:54.517" end="1:55.960">threats</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">带着暴力的字眼和恐吓威胁</span></p><p begin="1:56.129" end="2:00.695" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.129" end="1:56.371">And</span> <span begin="1:56.371" end="1:56.558">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:56.558" end="1:57.142">sick</span> <span begin="1:57.300" end="1:57.573">that</span> <span begin="1:57.573" end="1:58.266">all</span> <span begin="1:58.266" end="1:59.008">these</span> <span begin="1:59.008" end="2:00.695">battles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">令我厌恶的是</span></p><p begin="2:00.926" end="2:06.505" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.926" end="2:01.206">Are</span> <span begin="2:01.206" end="2:01.955">what</span> <span begin="2:01.955" end="2:02.683">keeps</span> <span begin="2:02.683" end="2:03.376">me</span> <span begin="2:03.754" end="2:06.505">satisfied</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些都让我心满意足</span></p><p begin="2:06.956" end="2:11.755" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.956" end="2:07.352">Just</span> <span begin="2:07.352" end="2:08.080">gonna</span> <span begin="2:08.080" end="2:08.815">stand</span> <span begin="2:08.815" end="2:09.186">there</span> <span begin="2:09.186" end="2:09.564">and</span> <span begin="2:09.564" end="2:10.138">watch</span> <span begin="2:10.138" end="2:10.593">me</span> <span begin="2:10.593" end="2:11.755">burn</span><sp